data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story four-bedroom home tucked away in a quiet cul-de-sac. This property boasts the added benefit of paid solar power, meaning no lease or monthly payments. The upgraded kitchen features modern appliances and ample storage space, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The open layout creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, ideal for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. Situated in an established neighborhood with no HOA, you'll enjoy a sense of community and freedom. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home!  The security system stays with the house.  One of the advantages of this property is that the seller's loan is assumable (VA), allowing potential buyers to take over the existing mortgage.
